trans-unit.source: Specifies the current stage of a [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] download operation.
trans-unit.target: Especifica a fase atual de um [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] transferir a operação.

trans-unit.source: DeploymentProgressState is passed by way of the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DownloadProgressChangedEventArgs.State%2A> member of <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs>, which is used by the <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>, and <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged> events.
trans-unit.target: DeploymentProgressState é transmitida por way do <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DownloadProgressChangedEventArgs.State%2A>membro <xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs>, que é utilizado pelo <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged>, <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged>, e <xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged>eventos.</xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.DownloadFileGroupProgressChanged> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.UpdateProgressChanged> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.ApplicationDeployment.CheckForUpdateProgressChanged> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.DeploymentProgressChangedEventArgs> </xref:System.Deployment.Application.DownloadProgressChangedEventArgs.State%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the members of this enumeration to determine what portion of the [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] deployment has already been downloaded to the local machine.
trans-unit.target: Utilize os membros desta enumeração para determinar que parte a [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] implementação já tenha sido transferida para o computador local.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)] is downloading the DLLs and data files that comprised the application.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)]está a transferir os ficheiros de DLLs e os dados que inclui a aplicação.
[!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)]está a transferir o manifesto da aplicação.
[!INCLUDE[ndptecclick](~/add/includes/ndptecclick-md.md)]está a transferir o manifesto de implementação.
